Package: XDocTools
Version: 0.1-0
Title: Tools for working with XML and XSL documents
Description: This is a package intended to provide
  helpful tools to facilitate authoring and working
  with XML documents. If one uses structured documents,
  one can use many powerful operations programmatically on these
  documents to query and modify the documents.  This package is 
  an attempt to collect some of these functions in a single place.
  Its is also intended to illustrate how easy it is to write powerful tools
  for processing structured documents.
License: BSD
Depends: methods, XML
Suggests: RCurl
Author: Duncan Temple Lang
Maintainer: Duncan Temple Lang <duncan@r-project.org>
